dm_morpheus Remake for CSS
=====================
Classic UT map rebuilt for CS Source:

Features:
UT Classic morpheus design
36 Random Spawns
Launcher On Mid Platform
Custom Textures + Custom Skybox

All embedded into BSP inv NAV file

======================
Hint:
Just before you hit the launch pad, jump
======================
Credits:
Original concept/design to the first compiletion, wether it be EA or any other indivudual who may have released it first, rebuilt in hammer for Source by mr-thermaltakexXxÂ©

Readme.txt Contains Other Information.

To successfully use this map you must use the following CVARS on your server.

sv_gravity 200
sv_airaccelerate 250
sv_friction 3

Zip contains mani CFG file which will automatically execute the settings for servers running mani admin
